{"tid":1870724,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"要記住","createTime":"2020-02-09T04:53:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-09T12:05:33.000Z","uid":198130,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"35b0edd555e2b4ba102a0fc25aa8ad0869d5b476","tid":1870724,"uid":198130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T04:53:28.000Z","msg":"有時我哋放唔開除咗因為失去之外<br />\n其實係心疼自己曾經嘅付出<br />\n遺忘嘅好處係 或者會后悔 或者會難過 <br />\n但係遺忘左之後心就唔會再痛<br />\n曾經睇唔慣受唔住<br />\n如今都不過係淡然一笑<br />\n成熟唔係看破 而係要去看淡<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28e8c1a0a0009feebd46e6823536cf0476e46fe9","tid":1870724,"uid":340796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T05:07:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62da148005acde082a18eb3f83c95b5334c7a367","tid":1870724,"uid":150930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T12:05:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}